For An Act To Be Entitled
8
9 AN ACT TO AMEND THE LAW CONCERNING CAPITAL MURDER,
10 MURDER IN THE FIRST DEGREE, AND MANSLAUGHTER; TO ADD
11 A MISDEMEANOR CONTROLLED SUBSTANCE OFFENSE TO THE
12 PREDICATE OFFENSES FOR CAPITAL MURDER, MURDER IN THE
13 FIRST DEGREE, AND MANSLAUGHTER; AND FOR OTHER
14 PURPOSES.
15
16
Subtitle
17
18 TO ADD A MISDEMEANOR CONTROLLED
19 SUBSTANCE OFFENSE TO THE PREDICATE
20 OFFENSES FOR CAPITAL MURDER, MURDER IN
21 THE FIRST DEGREE, AND MANSLAUGHTER.
22
23 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
24
25 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code § 5-10-101(a)(1), concerning predicate
26 felonies for capital murder, is amended to read as follows:
27 (1) Acting alone or with one (1) or more other persons:
28 (A) The person commits or attempts to commit:
29 (i) Terrorism, as defined in § 5-54-205;
30 (ii) Rape, § 5-14-103;
31 (iii) Kidnapping, § 5-11-102;
32 (iv) Vehicular piracy, § 5-11-105;
33 (v) Robbery, § 5-12-102;
34 (vi) Aggravated robbery, § 5-12-103;
35 (vii) Residential burglary, § 5-39-201(a);
36 (viii) Commercial burglary, § 5-39-201(b);
